						               													<description>A game of battles and conquests in which only Mugrugni can be heard.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this board game perfect for an evening with friends, you will lead one of the five tribes of wild boars to conquer the 40 districts of Genoa. You can choose the Sciacaeli, the Scignuri, the Beline, the Besughi and the Legere to defeat your enemies with cards, dice, strategy and ... fangs!  Immerse yourself in a game of conquests and battles where only your skill as a strategist will determine the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During his turn, the player moves his boar armies to take possession of the districts under the control of the opponents.&amp;#10;Battles are resolved by rolling dice and using cards to help the attack succeed. The player who manages to conquer all the territories designated for him at the beginning of the game or the player who has scored the most points wins&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(Publisher's description)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
